{"tid":1972190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[加速主義]一位小粉红的自我修养","createTime":"2020-04-14T11:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T15:26:13.000Z","uid":14480,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b42d8be2516d719890446d38918e1bcac2a1da5a","tid":1972190,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"泰支大戰，仲有動物森友會兩單野<br />\n見到其實只要有小粉紅係國際互通既Apps上面炒作<br />\n就會吸晒仇恨同令國際關注<br />\n亦都見到小粉紅既愛國愛黨，其實好易動搖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既係幫小粉紅係國際間增加仇恨值，<br />\n當中共知道小粉紅過左火既時候<br />\n就會下令支那人唔好再發表偉論<br />\n令到真實既小粉紅陷入【我愛國都有錯?】既迷思<br />\n<br />\n仲有，好似鳳凰衛視等等記者風波<br />\n證明支國根本係國際間唔敢同返支那個朵，只係敢叫自己做香港或台灣<br />\n身為小粉紅更應狙擊佢地不愛國！<br />\n總之就係批鬥<br />\n鬥愛國、鬥紅、鬥癲<br />\n<br />\n例子: <br />\n湾湾老是爱提天安门事件，难度就红眼我们屠杀一次，换来三十年高速发展?<br />\n现在超越了你们，死妈的孤儿们红眼了?<br />\n湾湾跟港毒就这种素质?<br />\n<br />\n有咁口臭，得咁口臭<br />\n唔好忘記，仲有港澳辦中聯辦踩晒屎<br />\n更應係國際間做小粉紅狂推<br />\n支持中國先於兩制，係黨既一國管治之下<br />\n基本法都只係廢紙<br />\n<br />\n單野往炒就只會往旺"},{"pid":"a57e49720a4d794ccb716172315613c8b78974ed","tid":1972190,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ca99049a956b152d249ec072a83b2eb7df77a5d","tid":1972190,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"根本就係要咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727a14b5652741ab6f5d9869e58ffc93d438bcb1","tid":1972190,"uid":76603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一起做个勇敢中国人 怼爆死妈港独"},{"pid":"7b964cd7ccfe4111811c1748ebd791239213bc6d","tid":1972190,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"不過要make sure唔會俾人check到係香港人暗黑兵法，如果唔係就變咗「台灣人」對譚德賽認錯咁，咁就7喇，響未諗到點做之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可以操住體能先<br />\n<br />\n[即時生效]以後邊個再鬥黃就原地做一set體能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da47a54d446904c883304542806f5e9abe6fb99f","tid":1972190,"uid":14480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ca99049a956b152d249ec072a83b2eb7df77a5d","tid":1972190,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"根本就係要咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"好多人仲係鬥緊黃<br />\n要鬥就同小粉紅鬥紅<br />\n係各OLG已好有效<br />\n反正連登仔鐘意玩膠<br />\n要玩就玩到盡<br />\n<br />\n我試過玩到真實小粉紅pm我圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87bcc8ebf4aaff4656a1dcfb2f95bc12be0710d","tid":1972190,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b964cd7ccfe4111811c1748ebd791239213bc6d","tid":1972190,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"不過要make sure唔會俾人check到係香港人暗黑兵法，如果唔係就變咗「台灣人」對譚德賽認錯咁，咁就7喇，響未諗到點做之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可以操住體能先<br />\n<br />\n[即時生效]以後邊個再鬥黃就原地做一set體能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:20:29.000Z","msg":"香港人一樣可以有小粉紅<br />\n我句例子係香港人口中講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f14c34791e8959e5f7b4ce37c3a7f9a593b475","tid":1972190,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d39c9401e1eb0ffe2f53b6e171ab489e0ee15b69","tid":1972190,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727a14b5652741ab6f5d9869e58ffc93d438bcb1","tid":1972190